{
  "stem": "512.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had a hard time because I was still also-- they gave me something that it was very short, changed it with somebody for a little longer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they marched us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to, to the, to the-- it was called, the camp, the Lager in German, the Lager.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I couldn't find my sister already because it was even hard to recognize anybody because the heads were shaved off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All you had to do is yell, scream.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was at night, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they brought us into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were in-- it was called Lager [GERMAN], C in English, C-Lager, in the block.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The barracks that we stayed was 20, 22, number 22.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They, they were the, the sort of beds that housed about 1,000 women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This put us in 10 to a bed with all you, all you were able to do is lay on one side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And at night, when everybody, everybody had to turn one way because there wasn't enough room, and it was a three-story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I know the bathroom, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the bathrooms, you were not allowed to go at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So there were young girls up there screaming, they had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They wouldn't allow them, so they urinated on the ones that were in the bottom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we  were all initiated, urinated on from the upper ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In the morning, somehow didn't sleep, but [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You started thinking, I'm missing everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I missing my parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I'm missing, I'm missing my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I found my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
